      <h1>GDRFA Family Visa Documents</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Translation and Attestation Checklist</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Sponsoring family members in the UAE requires specific documents for each relationship type. This guide covers the exact documents, attestation chains, and translation requirements for spouse, children, and parent visas — plus the common reasons applications get rejected.</p>

